import { ProductOne, ProductFour, ProductTheree,  ProductTwo } from './_Data';

const HomePage = () => {
    return (
        <>

            </Head>
            <Layout>
                <Slider/>
                <Container>
                    <ProductCard {...ProductOne}/>
                    <ProductCard {...ProductTwo}/>
                    <ProductCard {...ProductThere}/>

}

export default HomePage
